LOCUS       CmR                      219 aa                     UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  CmR is the 219-aa type I chloramphenicol acetyltransferase (CAT)
            from E. coli transposon Tn9, conferring chloramphenicol resistance
            by O-acetylating the antibiotic..
